About as close as I’ve got to this guy, maybe 30m give or take. with Minolta MC Tele Rokkor HF 300mm f4.5 handheld.
funny enough, that perch is not their nest, they made their nest on a light rack for a ball park, when the went south for the season, the ballpark built that perch (about 1/2 to 2/3 the height of their original) and moved the nest over to it. the birds came back in the spring and pretty much went “uh uh”, and promptly rebuilt their nest back on the light rack. they’ve been there since
